EXPERIENCE FLAGS for "new" style mobs

   The formula the game uses to determine the exp the monster has is:
        exp = BASE + (PHIT * (mob hp)/2) + (SAB * EXP FLAG+1)/2
   mob hp you set above, BASE, PHIT and SAB all depend on the mob's level.
   EXP FLAG you are setting here.  Do not set a value higher then 10 EVER!
   Final balancing of xp for mob "hardness" is at the discretion of the
   Lord of Worlds.  You should also consult with the L.o.W. to find out
   what mobs are of "equivalent difficulty" so you can ballpark your
